        "caption": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "Key Problems Identified"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Poorly designed dialog: Unclear \"Proceed\" button, no visible cancel option"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Example of problematic design: Ambiguous labels, low contrast, and missing safeguards."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Ambiguous labels (\"Proceed\" instead of \"Delete Account\").",
        "listType": "number"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "No confirmation dialogs, allowing irreversible actions to trigger instantly.",
        "listType": "number"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Accessibility failures: Low contrast, small click targets, missing focus states.",
        "listType": "number"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Inconsistent patterns across platforms (desktop vs. mobile).",
        "listType": "number"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
