      {
        "type": "h2",
        "text": "Solutions & Design Decisions"
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "Clear, Action-Oriented Labels"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Problem: Vague labels like “Proceed” confused users."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Solution:"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "We replaced ambiguous labels with explicit action verbs, such as:"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "“Delete My Account”",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "“Remove User”",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "“Cancel Subscription”",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "This increased user understanding and reduced hesitation during task completion."
      },
      {
        "type": "img",
        "url": "https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/052b5715-3363-4fe6-980e-3f0dd8222353/30e0ed24-8739-4698-b69a-77c2fde27af7/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466XECBUG5S%2F20260324%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20260324T204020Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjENP%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQCG9B754Y4jZ7Qv%2BZ%2BvgxKyE7vThmH3Orfb2DmNQvx4fgIhAJfXU6CoquER8FMxaje12smhNIRBAPp3qnxEzLTw2DVPKogECJz%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQABoMNjM3NDIzMTgzODA1IgxueM452wYBFKAcvXEq3AMwsBaF1knYxLF003Bz2b3CkTPGdIuoR47votN73vhGkZck8fLtZJPoSqbykhLZ4M8upvj73NLvDHHvmhLjeXXNaICjBn36DPoHEjc8D%2FtmTOkGiFCiBTBKwqYlNPXBEdnqBnNeDY7tjgYykdBsjpyWK16W4x04Z1sk3zvHNW8wGMoCCS3XAFVWxV%2BD3zGxDY3KyKx%2FY3uRRkK%2BbGLdErYmV1h7PZrq%2FovsHoSf5EoW1Ca7EIHUu8iaIW6FdhrG8QuGWT6WC2FYA6Kue9ZAAXlpMusUofbAPn6iGgSCbWha5lGy8UXbUW6%2BsMsnVkLO6reMmtTNequgWdK63DIbSJYYKqTYHsrG5f32P%2Bv5EhTNv4FcNLd%2BIpNc5lK8Me8baUklt47QZHTxjI1I93l8w32llm6B3iKyNScCUfitkiCWNvGNYjGH1JjGY4TeyVmP0mexr%2FDaQg%2BPOEW3QgJ8uSGytDFqnnoOga%2Bxl6LLGSLzk6mySuNffTwAoJRj9tLIMPN%2BIR37lSNlm%2FmL4HB19%2FWE9L8wWIgXI%2FFlcUTmbvWPbMUrSdh4oI512I0EbatVJeT8A7rMYvPlI%2Bh34vn4chsgZfgUVvR9CpmPK9KC4mwcbSE5O9aHgaAWo%2BXndzCHvIvOBjqkAVCkKLFKiTDLOVl2L9RWqTMnEIiyyIwHDa%2BVg%2F1E51ouIl%2Ba0lefCf1Y264NUpN0opKW31w4ZYdfkWsLgUuaKYub4x3cFrBh63rRPxohqkoBI8fU9RWVt%2FGm0sqHCNJgb%2FfN%2BYEfygfuK8HzT%2BYVSJTGx2OLp%2Bx%2Bi%2B3COnydMgw0VAJOEGVITsoDPvyKQsMxbP5mHGjAb%2FYtkkztbm0HBevgekXU&X-Amz-Signature=c9791637590c926cf10406c027956e1f09baf7d5190bbc88bd77779267b7bd5d&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&x-id=GetObject",
        "caption": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "✅ 2. Confirmation Dialogs"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Problem: Actions occurred immediately without warnings."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Solution:"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "We introduced confirmation modals that included:"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Clear warning messages about consequences",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Optional checkboxes for sensitive deletions",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Clear button options: “Cancel” (non-destructive), “Confirm Delete” (destructive)",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "✅ 3. Visual Differentiation"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Problem: Destructive buttons visually blended with other controls."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Solution:"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Used high-contrast red color with text + icon (e.g., 🗑️ DELETE)",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Avoided placing destructive actions next to primary buttons",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Styled destructive actions as secondary, except within confirmation dialogs",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "✅ 4. Accessibility Compliance"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Problem: Buttons failed to meet basic WCAG standards."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "Solution:"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "We updated destructive buttons to meet:"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Target size of at least 24×24px (WCAG 2.5.8)",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Contrast ratio ≥ 4.5:1 between text and background (WCAG 1.4.3)",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Focus visibility (WCAG 2.4.7) with clear outlines and spacing",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": "We also tested with assistive technologies to ensure compatibility."
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "Results"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "92% reduction in support tickets related to accidental deletion.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Improved task completion rates in usability tests.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Positive qualitative feedback from users: “I feel much safer using this now.”",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Design system updated with clear patterns for destructive actions, adopted across multiple teams.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "text": ""
      },
      {
        "type": "h3",
        "text": "Key Takeaways"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Destructive buttons must be designed with caution: clear labels, confirmation dialogs, and accessible styles are non-negotiable.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Accessibility is not a layer on top—it’s part of the design from the beginning.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      },
      {
        "type": "li",
        "text": "Small improvements (like button spacing and contrast) significantly impact user trust and safety.",
        "listType": "bullet"
      }
    ],
